ontent/2757296194/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757296194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757296194","tinyui":"/x/QgBZp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757296194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757296194/Archived+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757296194"}},{"id":"3063087149","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3063087149","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzA2MzA4NzE0OQ==","status":"current","title":"Facturación Electrónica","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":172688813},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3063087149","tinyui":"/x/LQCTtg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3063087149","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3063087149/Facturaci+n+Electr+nica","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3063087149"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"fcf8822b-e2e6-4bf3-be70-229b4d6e1d3e\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para agregar Facturaci&oacute;n Electr&oacute;nica en el Flujo de QR en VPos, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"606cb2c5c040cd0069d13bf7\" ri:local-id=\"07d936f9-e9ff-45c3-9dd2-8b5def9b0301\" /></ac:link>.</p><p>Las horas estimadas son: <strong>36 horas ~ 4.5 d&iacute;as</strong></p><p>Fecha estimada de inicio: <strong>L&uacute;nes </strong><time datetime=\"2025-06-09\" /> </p><p>Fecha estimada de Entrega: <strong>L&uacute;nes </strong><time datetime=\"2025-06-16\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p /><p /><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"1e3036f7-4a6e-4d1c-80e9-0ba8968a3a3d\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 156.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 428.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 176.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p /></th><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>vpos</p></td><td><p>Luego de enviar el pago para autorizar en endpoint de confirmaci&oacute;n de QR (<code>confirm_qr_buy</code>), encolar la generaci&oacute;n de la factura.</p><p><strong>Comentarios:</strong></p><p><em>Si la generaci&oacute;n de factura falla, no se genera la factura pero el pago permanece efectuado. El comercio deber&aacute; realizar la factura desde el portal de FE. </em><br /><em>Guardar en la tabla nueva el nro de factura y CDC.</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">18</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>vpos</p></td><td><p>Confirmar que el callback al comercio ya tiene la informacion del resultado de la generacion de factura..</p><p><strong>Comentarios:</strong></p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"396da334-c0cc-4443-9966-7ae8224e0956\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[        \"billing_response\": {\n            \"status\": \"success\",\n            \"description\": \"Factura generada correctamente\",\n            \"data\": {\n                \"invoice_number\": \"001-001-0002563\"\n            } \n        }]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>En el caso de que no se haya hecho el flujo de FE, no agregar el bloque en el callback, ni siquiera vac&iacute;o.<br /><br />En una revisi&oacute;n previa vimos que a priori ese c&oacute;digo se puede reutilizar sin problemas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">1</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>vpos</p></td><td><p>En la operaci&oacute;n de &ldquo;<code>confirm_qr_buy</code>&ldquo; devolver como par&aacute;metro opcional, los datos de billing.</p><p><strong>Comentarios:</strong></p><p><em>Estos par&aacute;metros solo se deben devolver si el comercio los pide.</em></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"176\" ac:original-width=\"520\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20250327-144253.png\" ac:width=\"412\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20250327-144253.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td><td><p>En la operaci&oacute;n de &ldquo;<code>confirm_qr_buy</code>&ldquo; devolver como par&aacute;metro opcional, los datos de billing.</p><p><strong>Comentarios:</strong></p><p><em>Estos par&aacute;metros solo se deben devolver si el comercio los pide.</em></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"176\" ac:original-width=\"520\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20250327-144253.png\" ac:width=\"412\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20250327-144253.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>Se contemplan en &eacute;stas horas el setup del nuevo proyecto y un breve onboarding</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Creaci&oacute;n y correci&oacute;n de PRs, y deploy a Staging</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">5</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">36</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4010999810"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":240},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4010999810/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4010999810/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4010999810/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4010999810/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4010999810","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4010999810/Flujo+de+QR+en+Facturaci+n+Electr+nica+en+VPos+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4010999810","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4010999810","tinyui":"/x/AgAT7w","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}